snippet.title: Huge Gap In Supply Of Currency Notes: Bank Officers Union

localized.description:
Harvinder Singh, general secretary of All India Bank Officers' Confederation (AIBOC), said that to completely restore the pre-November 8 cash situation, it may take two to three months.
